{"portal_release_date": "", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "", "catalog_type": "Data | Donn\u00e9es", "title_fra": "Fichier des activit\u00e9s li\u00e9s \u00e0 l'IITA de l'ACDI", "keywords": "", "data_series_issue_identification": "", "ready_to_publish": "", "id": "2f7e22f0-88f6-430c-9723-547043f898ad", "subject": "Information and Communications  Information et communication", "data_series_name_fra": "", "spatial_representation_type": "", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "Quarterly | Trimestriel", "title": "CIDA IATI Activity File", "author_email": "open-ouvert@tbs-sct.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Dans la norme de l'IITA, il est question d'\u00ab activit\u00e9s \u00bb, ce qui correspond aux projets dans le cas de l'ACDI. Le fichier sur les activit\u00e9s de l'ACDI donne de l'information sur les projets qui \u00e9taient actifs, en processus de fermeture ou ferm\u00e9s, en date du 31 d\u00e9cembre 2012 selon la Banque de projets. Ce fichier contient des champs de donn\u00e9es semblables \u00e0 ceux de la Banque de projets, exception faite des marqueurs politiques, dont la Banque ne tient pas compte pour l'instant.", "digital_object_identifier": "", "presentation_form": "", "spatial": "", "license_id": "ca-ogl-lgo", "resources": [{"name_fra": "Ensemble de donn\u00e9es", "language": "eng; CAN | fra; CAN", "format": "other", "url": "http://www.acdi-cida.gc.ca/iita-iati/acdi-cida_activites-activities.xml", "resource_type": "file", "name": "Dataset"}], "browse_graphic_url": "", "topic_category": "", "endpoint_url_fra": "", "date_published": "2012-10-31", "time_period_coverage_start": "", "data_series_name": "", "url_fra": "", "endpoint_url": "", "time_period_coverage_end": "", "language": "Bilingual (English and French) | Bilingue (Anglais et Fran\u00e7ais)", "date_modified": "2013-04-30", "url": "", "notes": "The IATI Standard refers to \"activities\", which for CIDA means projects. This file contains information on projects that were operational, terminating or closed, in the Project Browser on December 31, 2012. It contains data fields that are similar to those in the Project Browser, except for policy markers, which are not currently included in the Project Browser.", "owner_org": "cida-acdi", "keywords_fra": ""}
