{"owner_org": "9391E0A2-9717-4755-B548-4499C21F917B", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "1.0", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\u00e9o", "title_fra": "Toporama - 043E04", "keywords": "Toporama-043e04-6.0,Earth science,Administrative divisions,Buildings,Communications,Contours,Cultural features,Electricity,Terrain elevation,Land cover,Landforms,Pipelines,Topographical relief,Transportation,Vegetation,Wetlands,Administratives boundaries,Buildings and structures,Energy,Hydrography,Industrial and commercial areas,Places of interest,Relief and landforms,Toponymy - place names,Water saturated soils,Ontario,Tabasokwia lake,043e04", "data_series_issue_identification": "1.0", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "Toporama", "spatial_representation_type": "Grid | Grille", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "As Needed | Au besoin", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "geoginfo@NRCan.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Toporama est un produit num\u00e9rique de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence topographique produit par Ressources naturelles Canada (RNCan). Toporama couvre le territoire canadien et offre une information topographique, g\u00e9or\u00e9f\u00e9renc\u00e9e et symbolis\u00e9e en format matriciel. Le d\u00e9coupage, le contenu et la repr\u00e9sentation de ce produit sont similaires \u00e0 celui des cartes topographiques \u00e0 l'\u00e9chelle 1/50 000.  Toporama est publi\u00e9 sous forme d'\u00e9dition (\u00ab release \u00bb) selon un intervalle d'environ six mois. Toporama est distribu\u00e9 sans frais par l'entremise du portail G\u00e9oGratis (www.GeoGratis.gc.ca) dans le format matriciel GeoTIFF qui est un format matriciel g\u00e9or\u00e9f\u00e9renc\u00e9. Toporama est disponible dans les syst\u00e8mes de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence spatial suivants : universel transverse de Mercator (UTM) et g\u00e9ographique (latitude et longitude).  Toporama est un produit destin\u00e9 au grand public pouvant \u00eatre utilis\u00e9 notamment par les utilisateurs de syst\u00e8mes GPS qui ont besoin d'un produit cartographique matriciel g\u00e9or\u00e9f\u00e9renc\u00e9.", "id": "003adea3-3913-4f13-ad24-c842e41b3145", "presentation_form": "Map Digital | Carte num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[-88, 53], [-88, 53.25], [-87.5, 53.25], [-87.5, 53], [-88, 53]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "www.geogratis.gc.ca", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "www.geogratis.gc.ca", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/toporama/50k_geo_tif/043/e/toporama_043e04_geo.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/toporama/50k_geo_tif/043/e/toporama_043e04_geo.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/toporama/50k_utm_tif/043/e/toporama_043e04_utm.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/toporama/50k_utm_tif/043/e/toporama_043e04_utm.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "www.geogratis.gc.ca", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}], "browse_graphic_url": "http://www.fakeimageurl123.com/foo.jpg", "topic_category": "Imagery Base Maps Earth Cover  Imagerie carte de base couverture terrestre", "tags": [], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "2010-11-02", "time_period_coverage_start": "1970-01-01", "data_series_name": "Toporama", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "1970-01-01", "notes": "Toporama is a digital topographic reference product developed by Natural Resources Canada (NRCan). It covers the 