\"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[66.600083, -92.743904], [66.618652, -92.743713], [66.618572, -92.698552], [66.600003, -92.698778], [66.600083, -92.743904]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.gtif", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.tfw", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.tif", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/geott/eo_imagery/gcdb/W092/N66/N66d38mW092d49m_1.summary", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}], "browse_graphic_url": "http://www.fakeimageurl123.com/foo.jpg", "topic_category": "Location  Localisation", "tags": [], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "1983-08-03", "time_period_coverage_start": "", "data_series_name": "Ground Control Database, Canada", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "", "notes": "The Ground Control Database (GCDB) is a collection of geo-corrected aerial photo images (or chips) developed for the GIS and remote sensing community. The database provides accurate and useful information obtained from corrected aerial photos. This database can be used by the end-user as a fundamental data source for correction and validation of satellite, vector and raster data, as well as for map correcting and updating, analysis, modeling, and image processing. The GCDB was initially developed to supplement processing and/or correction of LANDSAT and SPOT data for value added satellite imagery products. Now, through GeoGratis, online access to the GCDB is offered as an efficient and cost effective method of delivery to the end-user.", "title": "Ground Control Database, Canada - N66d38mW092d49m_1", "keywords_fra": "G\u00e9omatique,Donn\u00e9es g\u00e9ographiques,Photographie,Photographie a\u00e9rienne,Imagerie et carte de base,Bdpc,Photo a\u00e9rienne,Points d-appui au sol,Snrc 56k10", "organization": "nrcan-rncan", "department_number": "115"}
{"owner_org": "9391E0A2-9717-4755-B548-4499C21F917B", "data_series_issue_identification_fra": "3.1", "catalog_type": "Geo Data | G\u00e9o", "title_fra": "Base nationale de donn\u00e9es topographiques (BNDT) - 063L05", "keywords": "Ntdb-063l05-3.1,Earth science,Land cover,Lakes,Terrain elevation,Vegetation cover,Buildings,Rivers - streams,Electricity,Transportation,Contours,Pipelines,Communications,Designated area,Road,Manmade features,Relief and landforms,Hydrography,Hypsography,Toponymy - place names,Electric network,Railroad network,Road network,Water saturated soils,Vegetation,Saskatchewan,Seager wheeler lake,063l05", "data_series_issue_identification": "3.1", "ready_to_publish": "0", "digital_object_identifier": "", "subject": "", "data_series_name_fra": "Base nationale de donn\u00e9es topographiques (BNDT)", "spatial_representation_type": "Vector | Vecteur", "maintenance_and_update_frequency": "As Needed | Au besoin", "author": "Natural Resources Canada | Ressources naturelles Canada", "author_email": "geoginfo@NRCan.gc.ca", "geographic_region": "", "notes_fra": "Cette collection est maintenant statique. Les utilisateurs actuels de la Base nationale de donn\u00e9es topographiques (BNDT) devraient envisager de faire la transition vers le produit CanVec. La Base nationale de donn\u00e9es topographiques (BNDT) est compos\u00e9e de donn\u00e9es num\u00e9riques vectorielles qui couvrent l'ensemble du territoire canadien. En num\u00e9risant et en structurant des milliers de cartes topographiques, G\u00e9omatique Canada a con\u00e7u un produit homog\u00e8ne et complet, fort utile dans une multitude de secteurs d'activit\u00e9s. La BNDT comprend des \u00e9l\u00e9ments comme les cours d'eau, les zones urbaines, les r\u00e9seaux ferroviaire et routier, la v\u00e9g\u00e9tation et le relief. La BNDT utilise comme unit\u00e9 organisationnelle le d\u00e9coupage r\u00e9gulier du Syst\u00e8me national de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence cartographique (SNRC), lui-m\u00eame bas\u00e9 sur le Syst\u00e8me de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence nord-am\u00e9ricain de 1983 (NAD83). Chaque fichier (jeu de donn\u00e9es) repr\u00e9sente une unit\u00e9 du SNRC \u00e0 l'\u00e9chelle de 1/50 000. Les donn\u00e9es num\u00e9riques sont repr\u00e9sent\u00e9es par des points, des lignes et des surfaces.", "id": "003bff35-0ce4-456c-b441-c3a3c937dae2", "presentation_form": "Map Digital | Carte num\u00e9rique", "spatial": "{\"type\": \"Polygon\", \"coordinates\": [[[54.2499938, -103.50001114], [54.2499962, -103.75000257], [54.2499925, -104.00000198], [54.499997, -104.00000722], [54.499998, -103.75001281], [54.4999955, -103.50001083], [54.2499938, -103.50001114]]]}", "license_id": "", "resources": [{"url": "www.geogratis.gc.ca", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "www.geogratis.gc.ca", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}, {"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/bndt/50k_shp_en/063/l/bndt_063l05_shp_en.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "SHAPE"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/bndt/50k_shp_en/063/l/bndt_063l05_shp_en.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "SHAPE"}, {"url": "http://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/bndt/50k_shp_fr/063/l/bndt_063l05_shp_fr.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "SHAPE"}, {"url": "ftp://ftp2.cits.rncan.gc.ca/pub/bndt/50k_shp_fr/063/l/bndt_063l05_shp_fr.zip", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "SHAPE"}, {"url": "www.geogratis.gc.ca", "resource_type": "file", "language": "eng; CAN", "format": "other"}], "browse_graphic_url": "http://www.fakeimageurl123.com/foo.jpg", "topic_category": "Imagery Base Maps Earth Cover  Imagerie carte de base couverture terrestre", "tags": [], "endpoint_url_fra": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/fr/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "date_published": "2010-11-02", "time_period_coverage_start": "1968-08-01", "data_series_name": "National Topographic Data Base (NTDB)", "endpoint_url": "http://geogratis.gc.ca/api/en/nrcan-rncan/ess-sst/", "time_period_coverage_end": "1968-08-01", "notes": "This collection is static now. Current users of the National Topographic Data Base (NTDB) should plan to make the transition towards CanVec product. The National Topographic Data Base (NTDB) comprises digital vector data sets that cover the entire Canadian landmass. Geomatics Canada has digitized and structured thousands of topographic maps, creating a complete and uniform product that can be highly useful in a broad range of industries. The NTDB includes features such as watercourses, urban areas, railways, roads, vegetation, and relief.The organizational unit for the NTDB is the National Topographic System (NTS), based on the North American Datum of 1983 (NAD83). Each file (data set) consists of one NTS unit at the 1:50,000 scale. The ground data is depicted through points, lines, and areas.", "title": "National Topographic Data Base (NTDB) - 063L05", "keywords_fra": "Bndt-063l05-3.1,Sciences de la terre,Utilisation - couverture des terres,Lacs,Altitude du relief,Couverture v\u00e9g\u00e9tale,B\u00e2timents,Rivi\u00e8res - cours d-eau,\u00c9lectricit\u00e9,Transport,Courbes,Pipelines,Communications,Aires d\u00e9sign\u00e9es,Chemin,Constructions,Relief et formes,Hydrographie,Hypsographie,Toponymie - noms de lieux,R\u00e9seau \u00e9lectrique,R\u00e9seau f\u00e9rroviaire,R\u00e9seau routier,Sols satur\u00e9s d-eau,V\u00e9g\u00e9tation,Saskatchewan,Seager wheeler lake,063l05", "organization": "nrcan-rncan", "department_number": "115"}
