od of delivery to the end-user.", "title": "Ground Control Database, Canada - N66d48mW098d24m_5", "keywords_fra": "G\u00e9omatique,Donn\u00e9es g\u00e9ographiques,Photographie,Photographie a\u00e9rienne,Imagerie et carte de base,Bdpc,Photo a\u00e9rienne,Points d-appui au sol,Snrc 66j16", "organization": "nrcan-rncan", "department_number": "115"}
